Telkom has launched its Big Deal for August 2018. The deal is a SmartBroadband Wireless 20GB+20GB LTE package which has been given a double-data bonus. Users receive the following with the Big Deal: Telkom stated that Night Surfer data is available from midnight to 07:00 every day, while the Huawei B315 features Wi-Fi connectivity which can handle up to 32 device connections. The latest special is available until 31 August 2018, or while stocks last, said Telkom. <span data-mce-type="bookmark" style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; overflow: hidden; line-height: 0;" class="mce_SELRES_start">﻿</span>